Chronological according to school founding/openingApproximate ranking from 10/20/30 years prior, new contestants receive a random ranking from old teams not represented in the current bracketsMy personal favorite is alphabetic distance from a randomly chosen name/word: choose a team at random (blind fold + dartboard is helpful), then using the first letter that team's name rank the rest according to alphabetic distance.Example: Randomly select team "Magpies". They are the overall winner. Team names with N and L come next, O and K third, etc.. Variations: alphabetic distance by star player's last name, coach's last name, etc..
